sheet.description:
When you perform for 1 minute, the creatures within 30 feet of you that can hear you are affected by one of the following effects of your choice;
			Fascinating Performance. You choose a target in the audience. You have advantage on the next Charisma (Deception, Intimidation, Persuasion) check you make against an affected target.
			Tavern Snarl. You have advantage on Dexterity (Sleight of Hand) checks against an affected target.
